children.value: Blindcap is the first swimming cap provided with a vibration system and Bluetooth connection to aid professional blind swimmers.
Because of this smart device linked to an app, the coach can notify the swimmers exactly when they have to turn.
The app was developed for Galaxy S7 and Gear S2 devices (smart watch) and it allows controlling the intelligent cap as well as showing swimmer stats and performance.

It is based in precise data mining technology and geared for both
  developers and companies.

The growth in smartphones use and geolocated technologies opens a new road of very useful information which can provide a very enriching point of view. CtOS Enabler allows to transform this unused data into valuable information.

_data.text:
Transform geolocation data into useful information

The market growth for mobile apps that use geolocation propitiates the existence of platforms in the Cloud which reduce the complexity and development time of these apps, taking all the workload related to geolocation.

Likewise, nowadays, we witness a constant increase in the use of Internet and mobile devices apps, which generate a great quantity of data and consumer information that is being wasted, and that would allow businesses to know better their clients and their own company.

For companies which have an application that uses geolocation, CtOS Enabler works as a business intelligence system that allows companies to readjust their business. CtOS Enabler achieves this by obtaining personalized use statistics of their applications and also provides an easy graphical panel to handle areas of influence and geolocated data inside them.

For app developers who use geolocation, CtOS Enabler offers a set of tools easy to integrate in their systems that allow an agile and fast development with a wide variety of geolocation functionalities, adding value to their product.

children.value:
Max Motor Dreams is a project that reunites software and hardware to
  create a cradle that conveys the feeling of a car moving. This way, your
  baby can go to sleep as easy and comfortable as if it was in the car.

Using motors connected to a Raspberry Pi that controls the cradle
  movement, and an app designed and developed to record the trips, we have
  created a system that processes the travel data and replicates it into
  information the cradle understands.

_data.text:
Max Motor Dreams is a project that reunites software and hardware to create a cradle that conveys the feeling of a car moving. This way, your baby can go to sleep as easy and comfortable as if it was in the car.

Using motors connected to a Raspberry Pi that controls the cradle movement, and an app designed and developed to record the trips, we have created a system that processes the travel data and replicates it into information the cradle understands.

children.value: What color do you envision for the future?
The IKEA - Next Gen: Seniors display, on which we worked together to design the software, was made accessible for testing in Madrid's Plaza de Colón for a week.
The system determines the color that represents your and your generation's outlook on the future through a series of inquiries and AI-based analysis.
This project is framed in the effort to adapt and work to enhance senior citizens' quality of life and cities.

children.value:
Wakkap is an online video game trading platform between players. It is
  especially designed as a secure spot to sell and buy videogames for all
  platforms.

Anyone can sign up in the platform and sell selecting from the huge
  database that Wakkap has. In a simple process, an offer can be made and
  the seller does not have to take the game anywhere, Wakkap has
  integrated payment and pick up APIs to make the experience the most
  comfortable possible. For buyers, it is also very easy. Anyone
  registered can buy a game, choosing by price and status, and the game
  goes directly delivered to the buyer’s address.

Wakkap is an online video game trading platform between players. It is especially designed as a secure spot to sell and buy videogames for all platforms.

For buyers, it is also very easy. Anyone registered can buy a game, choosing by price and status, and the game goes directly delivered to the buyer’s address.

children.value: Yrrealidad Aumentada se sitúa después del último capítulo de la primera temporada de la serie Yrreal de Playz disponible en RTVE Play. El jugador se pone en la piel de una agente de policía novata que irá recogiendo pistas en el parque de El Retiro de Madrid para descubrir el paradero de Lucía, la sospechosa enmascarada.

La primera decisión que tendrá que tomar y que marcará el desarrollo del juego es a qué policía acompañará en la investigación: ¿a Mario o a Andrea? Para jugar solo es necesario un smartphone y descargarse la app que está disponible en iOS y Android.

Para esta aventura transmedia hemos utilizado el motor de videojuegos Unity y para las escenas con realidad aumentada hemos usado ARCore y ARKit. Además, para lograr el máximo realismo en las animaciones de las escenas se ha usado el traje de motion capture, Perception Neuron.
